Torvonnilous</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukilmarfyrewynd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kilmar Fyrewynd</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Holy Defender</span><br>  Posts: 717<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/02 12:55:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15354.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Total Noob question about AGI</span><hr size=1> You receive an AC penalty when your AGI is under 75, I believe your AC will be 40 point lower at 74 AGI than it should be at 75 AGI.<br>
<br>
Let's say at 74 agi your AC is 1000, at 75 agi with the same exact equipment, your AC would be 1040, which is a HUGE difference.<br>
<br>
Numbers may be wrong, but it's a MASSIVE hit in AC nonetheless.<br>
<br>
