Torvonnilous</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 331<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/02 1:37:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15354.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Total Noob question about AGI</span><hr size=1> True magic numbers:<br>
Sta 100<br>
Agl 75.<br>
<br>
Semi-good magic numbers:<br>
Dex 100 (Proc rate increase.  Another reported at Dex 125 &amp; another at Dex 175.  I have not seen confirmation though.)<br>
Cha 105 (buying/selling.  Vital for Tradeskill work in the long run.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sadad>Sadad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/22/02 2:52:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15354.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Total Noob question about AGI</span><hr size=1> And remember that when you become encumbered your agi does go down, so keep that in mind.<br>
<br>
The best way I have found is to get the Cat O' Nine Tails from Kerra Ridge.<br>
<br>
After you zone in, go straight until you go over the bridge. Take a left immediately after the bridge. Walk a while and you should see a small Kerran named 'Catfisher'. This guy is for a Quellious paladin quest. In the end, there should be a dock. Swim out to the left where there is an island.<br>
<br>
Here there are a few Kerrans and Kerran Puma. I just killed them all to avoid any potential agro problems since I was kos anyway. Go to the right path a bit. There is a pit with a few Kerrans around it. There should be a shaman, a monk, and a kerran tiger spahi. Pull with with extreme caution, but of course if you're kos you don't need to pull at all. There are two tigers that will agro on you regardless of your Kerra faction and the Kerrans will assist them. This will result in a dead paladin.<br>
<br>
What I did was root park the monk and spahi in order to take out the shaman. She was an easy green at 30. The monk was next, but reroot the spahi first. Now the spahi, if he has the weapon you will see a whip. If not, you won't see the whip. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  It took me about 4 or 5 spawns to get a spahi with the whip. All in all a fairly easy camp at 30 if you know what you're doing.<br>
<br>
The whip procs the ranger/shaman spell Feet like cat, an agility buff. It procs often even with a very low dex (68dex). I really don't notice that much of a difference in procs now that I have 79 dex though. The weapon itself is a bit heavy, you might want some sort of weight reducing bag. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=15354.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=15354.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15354.topic&index=8><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=15354.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=15354.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15354.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15354.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump t